divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking for the big dipper while on a walk. I saw an object in the sky and i thought it was a metero shower. When the object moved to thin clouds close by the outter shape became more apparent a thin white on the outter edge of it, also a yellow Y-shape down the center which had a pale yellow color. The object just moved at a steady place into the clouds about 500 feet above my head. The ufo disappered into the clouds. During this event i could not believe what i was seeing. After i relized what it was i was excited to see this incredible experience.
Summary: Figure eight shaped, with point at each end, thin light around the other edge of ufo
